fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.xml

Class SEDAXMLEventReader

  • Object
    • SEDAXMLEventReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class SEDAXMLEventReader
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    The Class SEDAXMLEventReader.

    Wrapper class for XMLEventReader for high level functions used in all SEDA metadata readers. It can read either XML document, either XML fragments. It's based on WoodStox STAX objects.
